---
title: Chorizo, Parsley and Lemon-Butter Fettuccine with Parmesan
description: This is a dish that contradicts in all the right ways: it’s sharp yet buttery, flavourful yet fast. Be sure to use just the right amount of fettucine so that the flavour in the sauce sings, just as it should!
